# Terraform state / cache / lock files — never bake into image
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/*.tfstate.*
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars

# Terraform workspaces (runtime state, kept empty in VCS)
infra/gpu-vm/workspaces/*
!infra/gpu-vm/workspaces/.gitkeep

# Python / build artifacts
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage

# Local env / secrets
.env
**/.env.local
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# VCS / editor
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.claude/
**/.DS_Store

# Docs / tests not needed at runtime
docs/
**/tests/
*.md
